After reviewing online, we can't find energy consumption or carbon emission data for Claude models. 
Neither Anthropic company nor third-party studies(papers and blogs) provide estimates for Claude.

For GPT-5, no detailed or formal data could be found. 
The available information mainly comes from blog posts and informal estimates,
And they are based on indirect assumptions rather than carefully measured data.

For Gemini models, available information is also limited.
While there are some blog estimates for Gemini 2.5 Pro and estimates for Gemini models as a whole, 
there's no detailed energy consumption data in the internet

